OL,3,CParents working from home 'makes
OL,4,Cchildren feel school is optional' -
OL,5,COfsted head
OL,7,FAccording to the same newspaper, Sir
OL,8,FMartyn said: "(After the pandemic)
OL,9,Fsuddenly people were used to working
OL,10,Ffrom home and, in many cases, I don't
OL,11,Fthink there was that same desire to
OL,12,Fhave their child in school while they
OL,13,Fwere at home.
OL,15,F"They had been used to it for the best
OL,16,Fpart of a year-and-a-half, on and off,
OL,17,Fduring lockdown. That changed
OL,18,Fsomething.
