OL,3,CParents working from home 'makes
OL,4,Cchildren feel school is optional' -
OL,5,COfsted head
OL,7,F"If my mum and dad were at home all
OL,8,Fday, would I want to get up and leave
OL,9,Fthe house, knowing they were both
OL,10,Fthere?
OL,12,F"I would be tempted to perhaps say,
OL,13,F'can I not stay with you?'.
OL,15,F"Seeing my dad go out early to work,
OL,16,Foften hours before I had even got up,
OL,17,Fwell, there's an expectation: put your
OL,18,Fshoes on, put your school uniform on
OL,19,Fand go out the door and go to school;
OL,20,Fgo to work."
